---
title: Venison Steak & Red Wine Jus with Thyme Hasselback Kūmara & Parmesan Baby Broccoli | Serves 4
description: Treat mum to a Mother’s Day feast fit for a queen! Juicy venison steak drizzled with a luxurious red wine jus pairs perfectly
with herby hasselback kūmara and cheesy greens. It’s the perfect meal to show her just how special she is.
